@Host = http://localhost:8080

### Ask the semantic cache
POST {{Host}}/api/langcache/ask HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "question": "How do I reset my password?"
}

### Ask a similar follow-up question (should be a cache hit)

POST {{Host}}/api/langcache/ask HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "question": "I forgot how to change my login password."
}

### Read cache stats
GET {{Host}}/api/langcache/stats HTTP/1.1
